<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA18">
<l>nāṉṟa mulaittalai nañcuṇ ṭuṟiveṇṇey</l>
<l>tōṉṟavuṇ ṭāṉveṉṟi cūḻkaḷiṟṟai – yūṉṟip</l>
<l>porutuṭaivu kaṇṭāṉum puḷḷiṉvāy kīṇṭāṉu</l>
<l>marutiṭaipōy maṇṇaḷanta māl</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who ate poison from the drooping breast [and] ate the butter</l>
<l>when it appeared in the netting, he who, pressing down [and] fighting the bull elephant intent on victory,</l>
<l>[finally] saw [it] break, and who tore the bird’s mouth,</l>
<l>is Māl who went between the myrobalan trees [and] measured the world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
